    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it left the showroom. From the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, every detail has been meticulously preserved. It\u2019s a rare find for anyone seeking a car that is essentially brand new\u2014don't miss out on this spectacular ride!",
