      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and the upholstery is in great shape with only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and all electronics function as intended. It represents a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, solid condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine starts up immediately and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides reliable shifting. The interior shows minor signs of regular use but remains clean and comfortable, and the exterior paint has a few light scratches consistent with its age. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative specimen, maintained to an impeccable standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This vehicle exhibits a pristine exterior finish complemented by an interior devoid of any discernible wear, reflecting a history of fastidious care and mechanical excellence. For the discerning buyer seeking an uncompromising driving experience, this motorcar represents the definitive benchmark in its category. We invite you to inspect this flawlessly preserved example of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 47800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this car. It's my absolute pride and joy, and it's in such incredible shape that it basically looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this thing from day one, and it really shows in every little detail. If you're looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, you've found it. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly synchronized double-VANOS system. The mechanical provenance is documented, including preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement. Shifting is handled by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual, feeding power to a tight factory limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are razor-sharp, benefiting from a complete suspension refresh using OEM components to eliminate bushing deflection. Finished in a mirror-like factory coat with an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this example represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a deep, mirror-like finish on its original factory paint with zero imperfections, swirling, or stone chips. The interior is a time capsule; the premium upholstery retains its original matte texture and 'new car' aroma, while every digital interface and tactile switch functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, open-checkbook service history and a pristine undercarriage. Every detail, from the crystal-clear headlight lenses to the unmarked alloy wheels, confirms its status as a collector-quality vehicle. This is an investment-grade example that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been curated and maintained to the most exacting standards. With its flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original luster, this motorcar offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its factory debut. A rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    }
